sources.title: Santa Fe Trail--HD quality upgrade
sources.description: This is a better copy than others of this movie i've found. This version was sourced from an out of print Spanish bluray, picture quality gained only a little above 480p. the larger 720p matroska encode is ready for anyone who wants to plug it into tsmuxer to create an avchd disc that'll fit a dual layer dvd or a bluray disc.
